    <body>
        <h1>Hello. We are AiForce.</h1>
        <h3>Our Story</h3>
        <p>
            AiForce was born from something simple — boredom. One ordinary afternoon, our founder sat staring at his desk, wondering what to build next. Instead of wasting the day, he decided to challenge himself: “What if I could create gadgets that don’t just work… but think?”

            <br />That spark of curiosity turned into AiForce.
        </p>
        <h3>Who We Are</h3>
        <p>
            We’re a team of makers, dreamers, and problem-solvers who believe technology should be exciting, not intimidating. At AiForce, we combine creativity with artificial intelligence to design gadgets that make everyday life smarter, cooler, and a whole lot more fun.
        </p>
        <h3>What We Do</h3>
        <p>
            From AI-powered personal assistants that actually get you, to smart tools that help with learning, productivity, and entertainment — our gadgets are built to feel futuristic, yet useful today.
        </p>
        <h3>Why AiForce?</h3>
        <p>
            Because we believe boredom can lead to brilliance. That first moment of “I’ve got nothing to do” turned into a mission: give people AI that inspires them, challenges them, and maybe even makes them smile.
        </p>

    </body>
